{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act17side", "eventName": "愚人號", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SN-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "海濱小道", "storyInfo": "蒂亞戈試圖說服喬迪離開，借此機會，蒂亞戈告知了喬迪關於格蘭法洛的一切。面對漆黑的大海，人們似乎無路可去。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutryinside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "fadetime": 3.0, "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬迪！", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......蒂亞戈叔叔......怎麼了嗎？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#8$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你......快收拾東西，準備離開這裡。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃、怎、怎麼了？我們要去哪？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "審判庭很快就會來這座小鎮。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......什麼？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些邪教徒，海裡的怪物，那些——", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#9$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們......要放棄這座小鎮嗎？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#9$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們？", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#6$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不，孩子，只有你要離開這裡，審判庭發現這裡有邪教徒之後，一定會找阿戈爾人的麻煩！", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不在乎那些邪教徒怎麼樣，也不在乎我們自己的命......我們在這裡生活了太久，我們不知道去其他地方該怎麼活下來，我們不會走。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你不一樣！你不是，一直想要看看外面的城市和風景嗎？你還年輕，你有天賦......", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是我、我......這太突然了。", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一個機會，喬迪，一個改變的機會，最後的機會。你得勇敢一點。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "留在這裡，遭受審判庭的訊問，就算僥倖回家，也不過是在對海浪與恐魚的擔憂中空度餘生。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可如果你離開......你的命運就握在了你自己的手裡，不是那座小小的禮拜堂。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那座禮拜堂太小了......你不該就這麼......", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂亞戈叔叔......我......可是這麼突然......", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別猶豫不決了，孩子，你要堅強些，更堅強些，就像你的父母和你的祖父母輩那樣。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我的父母，他們真的是為伊比利亞的事業奉獻了生命？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#5$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在說這幹什麼——快，來一起收拾。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#5$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#5$1", "name2": "char_empty", "focus": 3.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，太久沒見遊商，都是些舊衣裳......年輕的小夥子想要穿一身新，還要費那麼大力氣......離開不好嗎？", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1", "name2": "char_empty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是審判庭為什麼要抓阿戈爾人？如果真有邪教徒，就沒可能是黎博利、菲林之類的嗎？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1", "name2": "char_empty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿戈爾人從海裡來，怪物和災難也從海裡來。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#9$1", "fadetime": 0.5, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你見過他們了？", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#9$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......我......等等，蒂亞戈叔叔，你知道......？你知道他們在這裡？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......我知道那些謠言不是空穴來風，我們都心知肚明。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胡安是他們的一員......他從小巷躲進陰暗無人的倉庫，他受傷了，而且......他對我沒有惡意。", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是因為你是個阿戈爾人，孩子。他們瘋了，他們不正常，我也清楚。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你為什麼......難道蒂亞戈叔叔是在包庇他們？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這都無所謂，你很快就要離開這裡了。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#13$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，蒂亞戈叔叔，我不想離開。", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#13$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#13$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我生在格蘭法洛，如果只是為了躲避審判庭就逃離這裡，我......我不知道......", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你什麼？你知道自己在說什麼嗎？！", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有阿戈爾人被帶去審判庭之後還能完好無損地回來！他們要嘛落下殘疾，要嘛精神失常——", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——更多人直接人間蒸發了，有人說審判庭囚禁了他們，也有人說審判官直接處死了那些嫌疑犯！總之沒有人回來，沒有人！", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#5$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那些怪物和深海教徒開始肆虐之前，“好心的”審判庭會先把這裡的一切付諸一炬，沒有什麼比毀滅更有效的淨化方法！", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#5$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂、蒂亞戈叔叔......冷靜點！", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怒髮衝冠的老人眼裡映出喬迪的模樣，就像多少年前他惴惴不安地來到這裡，想要從一片廢墟中親手建起新的庭院那樣。"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "半輩子過去了，一群年輕有力的人最黃金的年紀過去了，他們在格蘭法洛建立了什麼？伊比利亞如今怎樣？"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的添磚加瓦沒有對命運產生絲毫的影響，就像投進深井的石子，而曾經他們滿懷熱情建起的家園如今也搖搖欲墜。"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨大的虛無感吞沒了蒂亞戈。如同此刻海面上的陰雲，籠罩一切。"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒有人......", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有人......沒有人回來，馬琳沒有，他們都沒有。格蘭法洛已經在燃燒了，審判庭也好，怪物也好，我們沒有出路......", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂亞戈叔叔......", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......喬迪，你如果出了什麼事，我沒法向你的父母交代。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我......我知道。我......", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想去......看看海，可以嗎？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_4042_lumen_1#5$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibchurch", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 20.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘎——嘎啊啊啊啊——！", "name": "寡言的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.6}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在恐懼中昏厥，你們的夢境不會好受。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希，他們交給我。很快他們就會坦白，那些陰暗潮濕的陰謀盤踞何處。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（哇哦，這個酷老頭和你是一夥的？醫生？）", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們就是......日落即逝。搖滾樂隊，我不理解這些年輕人的玩意。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我希望你將其理解為音樂的神聖性。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "近幾百年伊比利亞都不曾有直接目睹巨獸的記錄，更妄言交流，若你們的音樂意味著你們對人類社會的看法，我倒是頗有興趣。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "《海中深色》之後，我們就沒有把注意力放在這些熟悉到失去興趣的事情上了哦。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1", "name2": "npc_2004_Alty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵......我很好奇在你們眼中，伊比利亞是什麼音色。看來漫長的生命還是可以為我帶來一些驚喜。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼凱爾希，如我們先前所說的那樣，審判庭會儘快為你準備好前往伊比利亞之眼的手段。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那之前準備好，然後盡可能掃清所有的障礙。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2004_Alty"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那隻恐魚，對，就是現在嵌在那個怪人身體裡的那個。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它身上有阿戈爾人的氣味。不一樣的阿戈爾人，接近我們的氣味，海的氣味。", "name": "Alty"}, "figure_art": "npc_2004_Alty"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1#2"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......什麼？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#2"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g18_lighthouse_square", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope02_intro", "key": "$newhope02_loop", "volume": 0.1}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂亞戈的步幅很小，但快。他顯得有些衰老，但又有一股莫名的精神。"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 5.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g16_lighthouse_street", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬迪勉強跟隨著蒂亞戈的步伐。他說，他想去看海。"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不知道自己為什麼要這麼說。就像現在，他不確定是自己想要去，還是蒂亞戈叔叔想要去海邊。"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g17_lighthouse_alley", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4042_lumen_1#2$1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是個阿戈爾人。喬迪想。海洋是我的家鄉。"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是我怎麼在海裡呼吸呢？那些島民祖先，利用怎樣的科技在水下生活呢？"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個接一個的問題回到了青年的腦海。小的時候他就對這些問題深感好奇，可是蒂亞戈叔叔回答不了他。蒂亞戈叔叔是個黎博利。"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "可始終號稱來自海洋的阿戈爾人，為什麼會溺斃在海洋之中？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i29", "x": 100.0, "y": 120.0, "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海......", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經記不得，上一次看見海面是什麼時候了......", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果懲戒軍還在這裡，那麼我們現在已經要被帶走盤問了。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱、抱歉，提了這樣的要求......", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒事。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 20.0, "duration": 15.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看這海岸線吧......荒涼，頹廢。幾十年前我們曾經有個偉大的計畫，這裡本該是固若金湯的堡壘。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在呢？東北面幾公里外有一處懲戒軍的哨所，西面的懸崖那頭還有一座。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除此之外？只有一個騙局......或者是一個夢。眼前這就叫現實，提醒我們，伊比利亞一去不復返了。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_whistle"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂亞戈吹了聲口哨。喬迪很少見到蒂亞戈如此輕浮的舉動。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此時他似乎變換了一種身份，從一個壓抑的鎮長轉變為了一個......工人。建設家園的工人，熱血沸騰的工人。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啐。都過去了。我們失敗了，格蘭法洛是失敗者的搖籃。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你之前提到了你的父母，對吧孩子？", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是的。", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對海洋......沒太多印象。雖然大家都說阿戈爾人，島民，但我不明白，我生在陸地上。", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yTo": 40.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScale": 0.9, "yScale": 0.9, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，你的父母，嚴格來說，是你的祖父母，來自阿戈爾，來自海洋的深處，那裡有一個浩大的國家。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來自那裡，孩子。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......阿戈爾。", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早些時候，在我們的夢想裡，格蘭法洛不是一座今天這樣了無生機的城鎮，它該是一座堡壘。一處堅固的據點。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會以這裡為起點，修建海岸防禦；我們會親手為國家阻隔災難，親手讓國家從災難中復甦，親手重建家園。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們曾經真的是這麼想的，孩子。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬迪沒有出聲打斷。蒂亞戈的神色逐漸激動起來，某種光彩回到了這個老人混濁的眼中。"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的每一寸肌膚都立了起來，他稍稍換了一個姿勢，海風揚起他的眉眼，他顯得高大了些。"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而作為那個橫跨半個世紀的宏偉藍圖的最後一步，我們將回到伊比利亞之眼。重啟那座......燈塔。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......燈塔？", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "燈塔，孩子。那是黃金時代的遺產，一個僥倖沒有被大靜謐摧毀的獨孤。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "災難都沒能摧垮我們，我們一往無前，懷揣著堅定的希望。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時候......馬琳戴著那頂藍色的帽子，她說......我們都是英雄。我們都將永垂不朽。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的祖父母，你的父母，喬迪，格蘭法洛的兩代人，他們都曾為了這個藍圖努力。他們本該......永遠偉大，真的。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是這裡什麼都不剩。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看見那艘船了嗎，港口本來有許多的船。那本該被懲戒軍帶走的，他們連這都忘記了。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些應有的東西什麼都不剩，剩下一些垃圾，一座不起眼的小鎮，數不清的麻煩，找不到出路的人，和......", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......和那艘船。", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......對。那艘船。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的父母，我沒見過的祖父母......他們對這份職責感到驕傲嗎？", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬迪，你不是第一次問這個問題。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還記得你剛懂事的時候，你剛決定留在禮拜堂做護工的時候......你都問過我。指著家裡那些塵封的手冊和圖紙，你問過我很多次。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......呃，我記得。", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。孩子。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你問我幾次，我都會告訴你，“是的”。無論結果如何，他們都在那場巨大的災厄之後還保持希望，為之奉獻。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我們最後一次嘗試前往伊比利亞之眼時，你的父母主動請纓。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要責怪他們拋下年幼的你......他們承載著所有人尚未消失殆盡的信念，已經過去太多年了，我們多需要一次成功啊。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......他們帶領的船隊從這裡離開土地，那是我們最後一次見到他們。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們是英雄，孩子。馬琳說，我們都該成為英雄，但現在我們都不是，只有死去的那些是了。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是嗎。", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的父親母親......", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是你知道，是什麼毀了這一切。在那樣的絕望中，我們都榨取出了所需的那丁點希望，指望點燃燈塔，結果呢？", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是審判庭毀了這一切。審判庭抓捕了阿戈爾人，審判庭說，我們之中蟄伏著深海教會的間諜。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們本該是為了伊比利亞而戰的。我們卻被該死的審判庭拆解得一乾二淨，尊嚴，理想，什麼都不剩下。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，你現在明白了嗎？", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你該離開這裡，你該遠離這毫無希望的伊比利亞，想辦法走遠一點......去外面的國家，去更廣闊的地方。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蘭法洛......什麼都不剩下。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g17_lighthouse_alley", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2002_Dan_1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大海！！", "name": "Dan"}, "figure_art": "npc_2002_Dan_1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這裡完全是反方向吧。我們就把樂器丟在那麼潮濕的房間裡？", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1", "name2": "npc_2002_Dan_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，Aya，這裡確實是海，我已經能嗅到面前浪花的味道了。", "name": "Dan"}, "figure_art": "npc_2002_Dan_1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1", "name2": "npc_2002_Dan_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "浪花是什麼味道？", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1", "name2": "npc_2002_Dan_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "棉花的味道。", "name": "Dan"}, "figure_art": "npc_2002_Dan_1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1", "name2": "npc_2002_Dan_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用嗅覺的詞彙來表達視覺元素嗎......", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過......你說的沒錯，我們的眼前確實有一片大海。", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3", "name2": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3", "name2": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你們......", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿戈爾人。而且和那些生長在陸地上的阿戈爾人截然不同。嗯......你們就是那些奇怪的阿戈爾人。", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼稱呼來著？喔，深海獵人。", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭皺起了眉頭。她極少用如此複雜的方式——皺眉頭——來表露情緒。"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來自於深海獵人的預感，一個最出眾的執政官，阿戈爾技術人員，或是戰士的預感。"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3", "name2": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們是......日落即逝。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3", "name2": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道她們。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3", "name2": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，偶然。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼呀，這麼神神秘秘的......不過還是很高興阿戈爾人也能知道我們的名字。", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Alty她曾經因為你們留下的一些氣息去過那艘艦船，大概是那時候認識的吧。不過這樣直接見面，還是第一次。", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自我介紹一下吧，叫我Aya，日落即逝的主唱。這位是Dan，我們的鼓手。", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1", "name2": "npc_2002_Dan_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們好呀，海洋的來客。", "name": "Dan"}, "figure_art": "npc_2002_Dan_1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3", "name2": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——你們同屬於海洋，很高興認識你們。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抵達陸地之後，我曾在凱爾希那裡學習過一些關於你們的知識——關於你們陸上同族的知識。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1", "name2": "npc_2002_Dan_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......你要是說陸地上的話題，那“我們”暫且還算同族，留在海裡的可就說不準了。", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們是來做什麼的？找那個醫生？", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3", "name2": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是按時赴約。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們在找回到阿戈爾的方法。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1", "name2": "npc_2002_Dan_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回阿戈爾啊......你們三個，一起？", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#4", "name2": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不會輕易分開。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#4"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，感情真好。那後面那位呢？難道是害羞了嗎，幹嘛一言不發？", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1", "focus": 3.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "幽靈鯊？"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看得出，她不太穩定，有什麼在折磨她的大腦。她病了？", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3", "name2": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "病了，也可以這麼說。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1", "name2": "npc_2002_Dan_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真可憐。", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1", "name2": "npc_2002_Dan_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——唔！", "name": "Dan"}, "figure_art": "npc_2002_Dan_1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1", "name2": "npc_2002_Dan_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，Dan？", "name": "Aya"}, "figure_art": "npc_2001_Aya_1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_2001_Aya_1", "name2": "npc_2002_Dan_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼穿過了我的脊髓，就那種感覺，腦門過電，然後意識到一些自己也說不上來的——", "name": "Dan"}, "figure_art": "npc_2002_Dan_1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——聲音。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反常沉默的幽靈鯊此刻凝視著天空。"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sea", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她閉上雙眼。混沌的思緒被浪聲沖刷，浪聲，這裡離海岸很遠，但有什麼正在觸碰幽靈鯊的意識。"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它在風中，躲在雲層裡，越過陸地，來自海洋。"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聲音。我能聽見。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聲音......？我沒有聽到什麼聲音。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海的旋律，海的子嗣在哭啼。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是......歌。一種歌。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#8"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是恐魚的氣息，越來越多，小鎮遭到了襲擊。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#8"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g18_lighthouse_square", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等、等等......你是......你怎麼進來的？", "name": "慌張的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你、你是審判官？！你拖著的那是——", "name": "慌張的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回家去吧，鎮民。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這兩個人涉嫌與異教勾結，我以伊比利亞審判官的名義，履行職責。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開這裡，鎮民們，他們的血會引來敵人，你們不應當被捲進這場戰鬥之中。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "審、審判官？！審判官什麼時候來到這裡的——那些外人，那些外人是審判庭的眼線？", "name": "慌張的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我不是邪教徒！我和那些人沒有關係！", "name": "慌張的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你認識他們嗎？", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#10$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他、他們......胡安？是胡安？我早就覺得他可疑了，他——", "name": "慌張的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "足夠了。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#2$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必折磨自己的內心，回家去吧，記得鎖好門窗。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是、是——！", "name": "慌張的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_460_1#1$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#3$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......來吧，別躲藏了。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#3$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嘁......審判官......不，你是大審判官之一！", "name": "深海教徒A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼審判庭會出現在這裡？！", "name": "深海教徒B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿瑪雅和蒂亞戈都不見了，和那個阿戈爾人有關......？", "name": "深海教徒A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖......他殺了胡安！", "name": "深海教徒B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他還沒死。我還需要他開口回答。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們與我過去所見的敵人都不相同。你們意識清晰，你們受人指引。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，如果你們真的這麼清醒而不癲狂，你們更應該明白——", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——你們無法戰勝我。無法戰勝任何一位審判庭的勇猛戰士。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#3$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嘖......", "name": "深海教徒A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你們為何還要主動獻身？又為什麼要飛蛾撲火？", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#1$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邪惡的浪濤許諾了你們什麼？你們在這處幾近廢棄的海岸線盤算著什麼？", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#6$1"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......我有很多問題，伊比利亞的敵人們。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#2$1"}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願你們的神能替你們想出答案。", "name": "聖徒卡門"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_447_1#8$1"}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}